          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-391-310A-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-391-310A-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-391-310A-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-1" n="1">If there be Truth in w<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> you Sing</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-2" n="2">Such Godlike Virtues in y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> King,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-3" n="3">A Minister so filld w<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> Zeal</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-4" n="4">And Wisdom for y<hi rend="superscript">ẹ</hi> Common-Weal,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-5" n="5">If he w<hi rend="superscript">o</hi> in y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Chair presides</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-6" n="6">So steadily y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Senate guides,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-7" n="7">If others w<hi rend="superscript">m</hi> you make y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Theme</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-8" n="8">Are seconds in y<hi rend="superscript">s</hi> glorious Scheme,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-9" n="9">If ev'ry Peer w<hi rend="superscript">m</hi> you commend</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-10" n="10">To worth &amp; Learning is a Friend,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-11" n="11">If y<hi rend="superscript">s</hi> be true as you attest;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-12" n="12">W<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Land was ever half so blest!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-13" n="13">The Traders now \n·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·l\o longer cheat,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-14" n="14">No Falshood now among y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> great,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-15" n="15">Now on y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Bench fair Iustice shines,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-16" n="16">Her Scale to neither Side inclines,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-17" n="17">Now Pride &amp; Cruelty are flown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-18" n="18">And Mercy here exalts her\<hi rend="italics">del</hi>·e\ Throne,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-19" n="19">For such is good Example's Power,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-20" n="20">It does its Office ev'ry hour</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-21" n="21">Where Governors are good &amp; wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-22" n="22">Or else y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> truest Maxim lies:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-23" n="23">For y<hi rend="superscript">s</hi> we know, all Ancient Sages</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-24" n="24">Decree, y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> ad Exemplum Regis</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-25" n="25">Thro all y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Realm his Virtues run</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-26" n="26">Rip'ning &amp; kindling like y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Sun;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-27" n="27">If this be true then how much more,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-28" n="28">W<hi rend="superscript">n</hi> you have namd at least a score</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-29" n="29">Of Courtiers each in their Degree</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-30" n="30">If Possible as good as he.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-31" n="31">Or take it in a diff'rent view</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-32" n="32">I ask if w<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> you say be true,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-33" n="33">If you allow y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Present Age</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-34" n="34">Deserves y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Satire's keenest Rage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-35" n="35">If y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> same Universal Passion</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-36" n="36">W<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> ev'ry vice hath filld y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Nation</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-37" n="37">If Virtue d\are·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·oe\s not venture down,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-38" n="38">But just a step below y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Crown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-39" n="39">If Clergymen to shew y<hi rend="superscript">eir</hi> Wit</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-40" n="40">Prize Classics more y<hi rend="superscript">n</hi> Sacred Writ,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-41" n="41">If Bankrupts w<hi rend="superscript">n</hi> y<hi rend="superscript">ey</hi> are undone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-42" n="42">Into y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Senate-House can run,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-43" n="43">And sell y<hi rend="superscript">eir</hi> Votes at such a rate</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-44" n="44">As will retrieve a lost Estate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-45" n="45">If Law be such a partial Whore</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-46" n="46">To spare y<hi rend="superscript">ẹ</hi> Rich &amp; Plague y<hi rend="superscript">e </hi>Po\o·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·we\r,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-47" n="47">If these be of all Crimes y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> worst</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-391-310A-line-48" n="48">W<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Land was ever half so curst.</l>
          </lg>
